elements.name: Validate searching of headphones after login

steps.name: I'm on the home page "https://www.ebay.com.au/" of ebay website
I click on the "Sign in" for Sign in link
type the "Email" for inputting email address,
I'll click on "Sign In" for second time signing,
I go to the "Search for anything" bar,
I'll click on "Search" for searching the headphone,
I will click on the "first Bose Headphone" to get the first Bose Headphone,
I'll "Add to cart" for adding the item to the cart.
